WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: sw

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Translator: Sophia Mwema
Reviewer: Nelson Simfukwe

00:00:12.844 --> 00:00:14.686
Tangu nilipokulia Kenya,

00:00:14.710 --> 00:00:17.261
nilijua nilitaka kusoma biokemia.

00:00:18.908 --> 00:00:24.439
Unaona, nilishuhudia madhara ya magonjwa kama malaria,

00:00:24.463 --> 00:00:27.156
na nilitaka kutafuta dawa ya kutibu wagonjwa.

00:00:27.585 --> 00:00:28.970
Hivyo nilijituma kwa bidii,

00:00:28.994 --> 00:00:32.781
nikapata udhamini kutoka Marekani, 
ambapo nilikuwa mtafiti wa kansa

00:00:32.805 --> 00:00:34.034
na nilipenda kazi yangu.

00:00:34.432 --> 00:00:36.519
Kwa mtu anayetaka kutibu magonjwa,

00:00:36.543 --> 00:00:38.254
hakuna wito mkubwa zaidi.

00:00:39.141 --> 00:00:42.493
Miaka kumi baadaye, nilirudi
Kenya kwa kufanya hilo tu.

00:00:43.021 --> 00:00:44.982
msomi mwenye PhD,

00:00:45.006 --> 00:00:47.207
tayari kupambana na ugonjwa huu kutisha,

00:00:47.231 --> 00:00:50.142
ambao ulikuwa kama adhabu ya kifo
kwa hakika kwa Kenya.

00:00:51.421 --> 00:00:54.372
Badala ya kuchukua kazi
katika kampuni ya madawa

00:00:54.396 --> 00:00:56.285
au hospitali,

00:00:56.309 --> 00:00:58.681
Nilijikuta nikiitikia wito katika maabara tofauti,

00:00:59.186 --> 00:01:01.562
kutibu mgonjwa wa aina nyingine --

00:01:01.586 --> 00:01:03.940
mgonjwa ambaye ugonjwa wake ulikuwa mkubwa

00:01:03.964 --> 00:01:06.849
na kuathiri kila mtu katika nchi yangu;

00:01:07.438 --> 00:01:09.778
mgonjwa aliyehitaji kuponwya upesi.

00:01:10.148 --> 00:01:12.551
Mgonjwa huyo alikuwa serikali yangu.

00:01:13.946 --> 00:01:15.096
(Vicheko)

00:01:15.922 --> 00:01:19.524
Tazama, wengi wetu tunakubaliana kwamba serikali zetu leo zina afya mbovu.

00:01:20.696 --> 00:01:22.779
(Vicheko)

00:01:22.803 --> 00:01:27.437
(Makofi)

00:01:28.634 --> 00:01:30.376
Na Kenya haina upekee.

00:01:30.795 --> 00:01:33.298
Niliporudi Kenya mwaka 2014,

00:01:33.322 --> 00:01:36.026
asilimia 17 ya vijana hawakuwa na ajira.

00:01:36.605 --> 00:01:38.953
Na Nairobi, kitovu kuu cha biashara ,

00:01:38.977 --> 00:01:43.052
ilikuwa ya 177 kwa ubora wa maisha duniani.

00:01:43.076 --> 00:01:44.280
hali Ilikuwa mbaya.

00:01:46.090 --> 00:01:50.549
Sasa, afya ya uchumi inategemea afya ya mashirika ambayo huifanya.

00:01:51.007 --> 00:01:52.157
Hivyo serikali -

00:01:52.181 --> 00:01:53.926
moja ya taasisi zake muhimu -

00:01:53.950 --> 00:01:55.388
inapokuwa dhaifu au ina afya mbaya,

00:01:55.412 --> 00:01:57.395
kila mtu na kila kitu vinateseka.

00:01:58.342 --> 00:02:01.115
Wakati mwingine unaweza kuweka plasta

00:02:01.139 --> 00:02:03.651
kujaribu kupunguza maumivu kwa muda

00:02:04.552 --> 00:02:06.534
Labda baadhi yenu hapa mmeshiriki

00:02:06.558 --> 00:02:09.537
katika wimbi la utoaji misaada Afrika --

00:02:09.561 --> 00:02:14.043
kuanzisha shule mbadala,
kujenga hospitali, kuchimba visima --

00:02:14.067 --> 00:02:17.004
kwa sababu serikali hazikutaka ama hazikuweza

00:02:17.028 --> 00:02:18.997
kuhudumia wananchi wao.

00:02:19.720 --> 00:02:22.529
Sote tunajua haya masuluhisho ni ya muda mfupi.

00:02:23.275 --> 00:02:26.060
Kuna baadhi ya mambo ambayo misaada haiwezi kutatua,

00:02:26.847 --> 00:02:31.236
kama kujenga mazingira
ambapo wafanyabiashara hujisikia salama

00:02:31.260 --> 00:02:33.071
kuwa watakuwa na fursa sawa

00:02:33.095 --> 00:02:36.337
kuweza kuanza na kuendesha 
biashara zao kwa ufanisi.

00:02:36.361 --> 00:02:38.175
Au kuna mifumo

00:02:38.199 --> 00:02:41.240
ambayo huwawezesha kulinda mali walizovuna.

00:02:41.264 --> 00:02:42.421
Ningependa kusema,

00:02:42.445 --> 00:02:45.889
Serikali pekee ndiyo inaweza kujenga
mazingira muhimu

00:02:45.913 --> 00:02:47.564
kwa ajili ya ustawi wa uchumi.

00:02:48.369 --> 00:02:53.207
Uchumi hustawi pale biashara zinaweza kuanzishwa kwa urahisi.

00:02:53.231 --> 00:02:56.603
wamiliki wa biashara hujiekea vyanzo vipya vya mapato,

00:02:56.627 --> 00:02:59.078
ajira zinazoongezwa katika uchumi

00:02:59.102 --> 00:03:02.666
na mapato ya kodi ili kufadhili miradi ya umma.

00:03:03.324 --> 00:03:05.787
Biashara mpya zinamnufaisha kila mtu.

00:03:06.235 --> 00:03:09.065
Na ni kipimo muhimu cha ukuaji wa uchumi,

00:03:09.089 --> 00:03:13.040
Benki ya Dunia ina kipimo kinachotwa
"Mazingira ya Kufanya Biashara,"

00:03:13.064 --> 00:03:16.101
ambacho hulinganisha urahisi
au ugumu wa kuanzisha biashara

00:03:16.125 --> 00:03:17.722
katika nchi yoyote.

00:03:17.746 --> 00:03:19.365
Na kama unavyofikiria,

00:03:20.224 --> 00:03:23.845
kuanzisha au kuendesha biashara
katika nchi ambayo serikali ni mgonjwa --

00:03:23.869 --> 00:03:25.318
karibia haiwezekani.

00:03:26.252 --> 00:03:29.976
Rais wa Kenya alijua hili,
hivyo mwaka 2014,

00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:33.369
alikuja katika maabara yetu na kuomba tushirikiane naye

00:03:33.393 --> 00:03:36.663
kuisaidia Kenya katika ukuaji wa biashara.

00:03:37.509 --> 00:03:39.231
Aliweka lengo kuu:

00:03:39.598 --> 00:03:44.520
alitaka Kenya kuwa kati ya nchi 50 za juu katika kipimo hiki cha Benki ya Dunia.

00:03:44.987 --> 00:03:47.064
Mwaka 2014 alipokuja,

00:03:47.088 --> 00:03:51.414
Kenya ilikuwa ya 136 kati ya nchi 189.

00:03:51.891 --> 00:03:54.047
kazi yetu ilikuwa bayana.

00:03:55.412 --> 00:03:58.113
Bahati nzuri, alikuja kwa watu muafaka.

00:03:58.137 --> 00:04:00.464
Hatukuwa timu ya kutoa misaada tu.

00:04:00.488 --> 00:04:04.254
Sisi ni kundi la wanasayansi wa kompyuta, wanahisabati, wahandisi

00:04:04.278 --> 00:04:06.215
na mtafiti wa kansa,

00:04:06.239 --> 00:04:08.685
ambao tulielewa kwamba ili
kutibu ugonjwa

00:04:08.709 --> 00:04:10.783
katika mfumo kubwa kama serikali,

00:04:10.807 --> 00:04:13.207
tulibidi kuchunguza mwili mzima,

00:04:13.231 --> 00:04:16.318
kisha tulibudi kuchimba ndani zaidi katika viungo,

00:04:16.342 --> 00:04:17.675
katika tishu,

00:04:17.699 --> 00:04:19.201
kote hadi kwa seli mojamoja,

00:04:19.225 --> 00:04:21.562
ili tunaweza kuchunguza vizuri.

00:04:22.582 --> 00:04:25.413
Hivyo kwa maagizo ya Rais mwenyewe,

00:04:25.437 --> 00:04:28.550
tulianza na njia halisi kabisa ya kisayansi:

00:04:28.574 --> 00:04:29.749
kukusanya data

00:04:29.773 --> 00:04:31.860
data zote tulizoweza kupata--

00:04:31.884 --> 00:04:33.141
kuunda nadharia,

00:04:33.165 --> 00:04:34.402
kutafuta ufumbuzi,

00:04:34.426 --> 00:04:35.618
mmoja baada nyingine.

00:04:36.665 --> 00:04:40.700
Hivyo tulikutana na mamia ya watu waliofanya kazi katika mashirika ya serikali,

00:04:40.724 --> 00:04:44.660
kuanzia vyombo vya kodi, ardhi, kampuni za huduma,

00:04:44.684 --> 00:04:48.152
shirika kenya jukumu
la kusajili makampuni,

00:04:48.176 --> 00:04:51.775
na kwa kila mmoja yao, tuliwaangalia
kama walivyohudumia wateja wao ,

00:04:51.799 --> 00:04:56.412
tuliweka kumbukumbu ya michakato yao - mingi ilitegemea kazi ya mikono.

00:04:57.293 --> 00:05:00.749
Pia tulirudi kuangalia makaratasi ya kazi zao za awali

00:05:00.773 --> 00:05:02.941
kujaribu kuelewa vyema zaidi;

00:05:02.965 --> 00:05:06.315
kujaribu kutambua nini katika mwili
hakifanyi kazi vizor

00:05:06.339 --> 00:05:09.647
na kusababisha kuwa ya 136 katika orodha ya Benki ya Dunia.

00:05:10.068 --> 00:05:11.371
Tuligundua nini?

00:05:11.794 --> 00:05:15.865
Naam, ilichukua siku 72 kwa

00:05:15.889 --> 00:05:18.833
mfanyabiashara kusajili mali yake Kenya,

00:05:18.857 --> 00:05:21.254
ikilinganishwa na siku moja tu katika New Zealand,

00:05:21.278 --> 00:05:23.656
ambayo ilikuwa ya pili
katika orodha Benki ya Dunia.

00:05:24.647 --> 00:05:29.032
Ilichukua siku 158 kupata umeme.

00:05:29.699 --> 00:05:32.131
Korea, ilichukua siku 18.

00:05:32.804 --> 00:05:34.857
Ukitaka kibali cha ujenzi

00:05:34.881 --> 00:05:36.401
ili kuweza kujenga,

00:05:36.425 --> 00:05:39.996
Kenya, ilikuchukua siku 125.

00:05:40.020 --> 00:05:44.466
Katika Singapore, ambayo ni nafasi ya kwanza, ilichukua siku 26.

00:05:45.400 --> 00:05:47.444
Hasha, ikubidi uenda mahakamani

00:05:47.468 --> 00:05:51.355
kupata msaada kutatua mzozo na kutekeleza mkataba,

00:05:51.379 --> 00:05:55.660
kwa sababu mchakato peke yake tu
utachukua siku 465.

00:05:56.885 --> 00:05:58.817
Na kama hiyo halikuwa mbaya,

00:06:00.495 --> 00:06:04.647
utapoteza asilimia 40 ya madai yako katika ada tu --

00:06:04.671 --> 00:06:07.543
gharama ya kisheria, ya utekelezaji, ya mahakama.

00:06:08.928 --> 00:06:11.001
Sasa, najua kile unachofikiri:

00:06:12.546 --> 00:06:16.213
ili kuwepo na uhaba huo wa ufanisi
katika nchi ya kiafrika,

00:06:16.237 --> 00:06:17.597
lazima kuwe na rushwa.

00:06:18.311 --> 00:06:21.787
Seli kuu husika lazima iwe inahusishwa na rushwa.

00:06:22.792 --> 00:06:24.324
Nilidhani hivyo, pia.

00:06:24.804 --> 00:06:25.957
Tulipoanza,

00:06:25.981 --> 00:06:29.469
Nilitarajia kukuta rushwa nyingi katika mfumo,

00:06:29.493 --> 00:06:32.989
Nilihisi ningekufa ama kuuawa katika mchakato.

00:06:33.013 --> 00:06:34.556
(Vicheko)

00:06:36.766 --> 00:06:38.721
Lakini tulipochunguza kiundani,

00:06:38.745 --> 00:06:41.380
hatukukuta rushwa katika maana ya kawaida:

00:06:41.926 --> 00:06:44.934
majambazi wakinyemea kwenye giza,

00:06:44.958 --> 00:06:47.275
wakisubiri lusaka mafuta mikono ya marafiki zao.

00:06:47.959 --> 00:06:51.945
Tulichogundua ni hisia kubwa ya unyonge.

00:06:53.504 --> 00:06:54.766
Serikali yetu ilikuwa mgonjwa,

00:06:54.790 --> 00:06:58.314
kwa sababu wafanyakazi wa serikali
walijiona wanyonge.

00:06:58.813 --> 00:07:01.896
Walihisi hawakuwa na uwezo wa kuendesha mabadiliko.

00:07:02.420 --> 00:07:06.056
Na watu wanapojisikia kukwama na wanyonge,

00:07:06.788 --> 00:07:09.283
huacha kuona majukumu yao katika mfumo mzimo.

00:07:10.085 --> 00:07:14.554
Huanza kufikiri kazi yao haijalishi katika kuendesha mabadiliko.

00:07:14.578 --> 00:07:16.384
Na hilo linapotokea,

00:07:16.408 --> 00:07:18.001
mambo huenda polepole,

00:07:18.025 --> 00:07:19.445
nyufa hujitokeza

00:07:19.469 --> 00:07:21.235
na ukosefu wa ufanisi hunawiri.

00:07:22.991 --> 00:07:24.756
Sasa fikiria na mimi,

00:07:24.780 --> 00:07:28.718
kama ulikuwa na mchakato ulibidi kufuata --

00:07:28.742 --> 00:07:30.512
na hukuwa na njia nyingine --

00:07:30.536 --> 00:07:33.583
na utaratibu huu ulikosa ufanisi, ulikuwa tata

00:07:34.281 --> 00:07:35.671
na taratibu mno.

00:07:35.695 --> 00:07:36.919
Ungefanya nini?

00:07:38.302 --> 00:07:41.630
Nadhani unaweza kujaribu
kutafuta mtu mwingine akufanyie hilo jukumu,

00:07:41.654 --> 00:07:43.999
ili tu wafanye kwa niaba yako.

00:07:44.620 --> 00:07:46.024
Kama hafanikiwi,

00:07:47.127 --> 00:07:49.137
labda utafikiria kumlipa mtu

00:07:49.161 --> 00:07:52.541
'kiholela' tu ili kufanya kwa niaba yako --

00:07:52.565 --> 00:07:55.323
hasa unapodhani hakuna mtu atakukamata.

00:07:56.610 --> 00:07:58.980
Sio kwa nia mbaya au uchoyo,

00:07:59.004 --> 00:08:02.095
ili tu kuhakikisha mambo yanakuendea vizuri

00:08:02.119 --> 00:08:03.277
ili uweze kuendelea na biashara zako.

00:08:03.738 --> 00:08:06.748
Kwa bahati mbaya, huo ndio mwanzo wa rushwa.

00:08:07.259 --> 00:08:09.582
Na kama ikiachwa kustawi na kukua,

00:08:09.606 --> 00:08:11.172
inavuja katika mfumo mzima,

00:08:11.196 --> 00:08:12.566
na kabla ya kujitambua,

00:08:12.590 --> 00:08:14.155
mwili mzima huumwa.

00:08:16.416 --> 00:08:17.709
Tukijua hili,

00:08:17.733 --> 00:08:19.288
tulianza kwa kuhakikisha

00:08:19.312 --> 00:08:23.889
kwamba kila mdau tuliyeshirikiana nae alikuwa na malengo kama yetu

00:08:23.913 --> 00:08:25.342
kwa ajili ya tulichotaka kutimiza.

00:08:26.012 --> 00:08:28.046
Hivyo tulikutana na kila mtu,

00:08:28.476 --> 00:08:31.035
kuanzia karani ambaye kazi yake pekee 
ni kufungua

00:08:31.059 --> 00:08:32.608
pakiti za maombi,

00:08:33.266 --> 00:08:36.251
hadi waandaaji wa sheria katika ofisi ya mwanasheria mkuu,

00:08:37.007 --> 00:08:40.004
kwa makarani mwenye wajibu
kwa kuwahudumia wamiliki wa biashara

00:08:40.028 --> 00:08:42.460
walipo kuja kupata huduma za serikali.

00:08:43.377 --> 00:08:44.527
Na pamoja nao,

00:08:44.551 --> 00:08:46.123
tulihakikisha kwamba walielewa

00:08:46.147 --> 00:08:50.894
jinsi matendo yao ya kila siku
huathiri uwezo wetu kama nchi

00:08:50.918 --> 00:08:53.993
kujenga ajira mpya na kuvutia uwekezaji.

00:08:54.425 --> 00:08:57.985
hakuna jukumu dogo; jukumu la kila mtu lilikuwa muhimu.

00:08:59.907 --> 00:09:01.782
Sasa, kisia tulianza kuona nini?

00:09:02.814 --> 00:09:04.827
Muungano wa wafanyakazi wa serikali

00:09:04.851 --> 00:09:06.963
wenye motisha wa kuleta mabadiliko,

00:09:06.987 --> 00:09:09.052
ulianza kukua na kuonekana.

00:09:09.747 --> 00:09:12.351
Na pamoja tuliaanza
kutekeleza mabadiliko

00:09:12.375 --> 00:09:15.607
yaliyoathiri utoaji wa huduma nchini.

00:09:16.405 --> 00:09:17.829
Matokeo?

00:09:17.853 --> 00:09:19.894
Katika miaka miwili tu,

00:09:19.918 --> 00:09:23.878
Kenya ilitoka kuwa ya 136 hadi ya 92.

00:09:24.844 --> 00:09:30.804
(Makofi)

00:09:32.340 --> 00:09:36.729
Na katika kutambua mageuzi tuliyoweza kutekeleza

00:09:36.753 --> 00:09:38.532
katika muda mfupi,

00:09:38.556 --> 00:09:40.437
Kenya ilitambuliwa

00:09:40.461 --> 00:09:44.047
kuwa miongoni mwa nchi tatu kimataifa
katika marekebisho

00:09:44.071 --> 00:09:45.487
miaka miwili mfululizo

00:09:46.518 --> 00:09:51.898
(Makofi)

00:09:52.984 --> 00:09:54.550
Je tuna afya nzuri kikamilifu?

00:09:55.376 --> 00:09:56.542
Hapana.

00:09:56.969 --> 00:09:59.401
Bado tuna kazi kubwa ya kufanya.

00:10:00.156 --> 00:10:03.633
Napenda kufikiria miaka hii miwili
kama harakati ya kupunguza uzito.

00:10:03.995 --> 00:10:05.571
(Vicheko)

00:10:06.341 --> 00:10:10.303
Ni ule muda baada ya miezi
ya bidii, na mazoezi makable,

00:10:10.327 --> 00:10:12.757
na kisha unapopima uzito kwa mara ya kwanza,

00:10:12.781 --> 00:10:14.445
na umepoteza paundi 20.

00:10:14.827 --> 00:10:16.609
Unajisikia hausimamishwiki.

00:10:18.517 --> 00:10:22.854
Sasa, baadhi yenu mnaweza kufikiria
hili haliwahusu.

00:10:22.878 --> 00:10:24.228
Wewe sio Mkenya.

00:10:24.252 --> 00:10:26.394
Huna nia ya kuwa mwekezaji.

00:10:26.418 --> 00:10:28.380
Lakini kufikiri na mimi japo mara moja tu.

00:10:29.134 --> 00:10:32.586
Lini mara ya mwisho
ulipotumia huduma ya serikali?

00:10:33.800 --> 00:10:36.576
Labda kupata leseni ya udereva,

00:10:36.600 --> 00:10:40.168
kufanya mahesabu ya kodi peke yako.

00:10:42.464 --> 00:10:45.234
Ni rahisi katika uchumi huu wa kisiasa
na dunia

00:10:45.258 --> 00:10:48.308
kutaka kukata tamaatunapofikiria kubadilisha serikali.

00:10:49.206 --> 00:10:52.707
Ni rahisi kujiuzulu kutoka kwa wajibu tu kwa kufikiria

00:10:52.731 --> 00:10:55.073
kuwa serikali haina ufanisi,

00:10:55.097 --> 00:10:56.253
ina rushwa mno,

00:10:56.277 --> 00:10:57.508
hairekebishiki.

00:10:58.347 --> 00:11:01.784
Huenda tukapata majukumu muhimu katika serikali

00:11:01.808 --> 00:11:03.008
katika sekta nyingine,

00:11:03.032 --> 00:11:04.201
katika suluhisho la utoaji misaada,

00:11:04.225 --> 00:11:06.793
au kukata tu tamaa na kujisikia wanyonge.

00:11:07.849 --> 00:11:11.732
Lakini, kwa sababu tu mfumo unaumwa haina maana unakufa.

00:11:12.509 --> 00:11:15.316
Hatuna starehe ya kukata tamaa

00:11:15.340 --> 00:11:18.373
inapohusu changamoto za kuzirekebisha 
serikali zetu.

00:11:19.809 --> 00:11:20.965
Hatimaye,

00:11:22.502 --> 00:11:26.677
serikali hula na afya pale tu ambapo seli huwa na afya--

00:11:26.701 --> 00:11:28.692
huyo ni wewe na mimi --

00:11:29.654 --> 00:11:31.301
kunuia,

00:11:31.325 --> 00:11:32.609
kukunja mkono ya mashati yetu,

00:11:32.633 --> 00:11:34.738
kukataa kuwa wanyonge

00:11:34.762 --> 00:11:36.558
na kuamini kuwa wakati mwingine,

00:11:36.582 --> 00:11:39.812
kinachoitajika ili kujenga nafasi, ni sisi,

00:11:39.836 --> 00:11:42.051
kwa ajili ya seli kukua na kustawi.

00:11:42.601 --> 00:11:43.758
Asante.

00:11:43.782 --> 00:11:50.021
(Makofi)

